name: "messirve"
description:
Ricardus
Ricardus is the fusion between Ricardo Fort & Frida Kahlo, each edition can also have a shout out to other iconic celebrities.
in this work you can appreciate clear references to Argentina and it is the first time that our character is not with a cigarette in his hand, has he quit? hopefully yes.
besides there is a shout out to maradona a little hidden, can you see it? the name makes reference to Messi's meme with sunglasses.
binaries and non binaries, with you, Ricardus #10.
